                <h2>What Are We Up To?</h2>
                <br>
                <p>We’ve created a cool website designed to keep you in the loop with everything happening at our college. Here’s what you can find:</p>
                <br>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Upcoming Events:</strong> Want to know what’s next? Check out the calendar for upcoming seminars, workshops, and social events. We’ve got all the details so you can plan ahead!</li>
